Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:49.75,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Everybody is naked before my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:53.20,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,I've seen everything that's been in your mind since we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:03:00.29,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,I've heard that you have a soft spot for women,\Nbut I didn't expect it to be this soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:02.16,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,How pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:06.48,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Your collar is all wrinkled and your tie is crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.48,0:03:08.10,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Your shirt is stained with blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.26,0:03:14.61,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,You look terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:19.52,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're a good-for-nothing man, "Black Foot" Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:24.68,Captions,,0,0,250,,{\fad(1000,0)}Donquixote Family (Tr√©bol Army)\NAssassin: Violet
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:24.68,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Did you really think that a guy like you could win my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:27.39,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,That's hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:34.73,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you were fooled by Sis' beauty, you stupid jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:38.88,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,You're lying, Violet-{\i0}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:44.80,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Hey, quit dreaming! Sis was just acting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:50.58,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,I-I know you have a beautiful heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:54.09,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Why are you still saying that after getting hurt so badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.09,0:03:56.24,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Hey, stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:01.60,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,You must have been coaxed into this by some bad guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:04.38,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,You don't even want to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:05.69,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,, Violet-{\i0}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:09.67,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Why don't you quit being so romantic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.81,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,So stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:24.79,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,That's terrible! But she's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:27.51,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,That was a hell of a kick, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:33.82,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,You're trying to hold back your anger\Nagainst me while looking for a way to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:40.11,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Did you think you could trick me with your lies?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:45.56,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Lies don't work on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:49.71,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,I ate the Glare Fruit and became an insight human.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.98,0:04:52.00,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,I can see through anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:56.45,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Men are all liars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:05:02.21,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,I'll let myself see what's in your head full of lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:06.52,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Why did Trafalgar Law and Straw Hat become allies?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:11.86,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,What are your goals, both on Green Bit and on Dressrosa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.86,0:05:15.76,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,What's your plan and what are you up to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.31,0:05:18.72,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,You don't have to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:22.90,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,All the answers are inside your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:25.97,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,We will catch all of your crewmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:28.01,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,It's coming! That pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:34.48,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Peeping Mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:45.09,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,W-W-What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:46.01,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.01,0:05:47.95,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,H-How perverted!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:50.42,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Perverted?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:54.40,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,I've never seen such an erotic mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:56.00,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:59.49,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,What about your plan?! Your true purpose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:04.68,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking under these circumstances?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.77,0:06:07.56,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:13.53,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,The way you looked at me at that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:16.98,Flashback inception,,0,0,0,,I want you to kill someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:22.63,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,I knew you were telling the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:29.25,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if a million people denounce you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:33.94,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to doubt a woman's tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:42.32,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,What a stupid thing to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:46.52,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,What a dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:52.19,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Sis, if this pervert is useless to us now, let's kill him and get it over with!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:56.16,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,A 77 million bounty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:07:00.28,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,A member of the Straw Hat Crew! The head of "Black Foot" Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:02.60,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Let's collect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:05.04,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Hierro Lagrima!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:05.04,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Iron Tear
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:09.21,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Sis, what're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:10.38,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Eye Whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:32.63,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Violet-{\i0}chan{\i0}, you really were working for Doflamingo against your will, weren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:37.94,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Run, Black Foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.94,0:07:39.84,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Violet-chan, what about you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:41.61,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Forget about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:43.14,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:50.55,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,We know what you people have been doing all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:55.65,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,I was your enemy but you kept believing in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:08:01.96,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,You really are a good-for-nothing man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:06.20,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your concern back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:10.64,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,It made me so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:15.91,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,I don't know the situation, but you don't want to work for Doflamingo, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:17.93,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,You even fought your own men!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:20.41,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Let's escape from this island together on our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:23.75,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Look at me, Black Foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:28.62,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,From the moment you all arrived here with Caesar,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:31.37,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,you were walking into that man's trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:32.19,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:34.58,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Look inside my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:43.97,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,What you see is Dressrosa this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:52.65,Flashback inception,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:54.83,Flashback inception,,0,0,0,,Don't say you quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:57.35,Flashback inception,,0,0,0,,Doflamingo-{\i0}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:08:58.95,Flashback inception,,0,0,0,,Please explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:09:01.99,Flashback inception,,0,0,0,,Why did you abdicate from the throne?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.45,0:09:09.16,Flashback inception,,0,0,0,,How noisy. Aren't they here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.77,Flashback inception,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:18.35,Flashback inception,,0,0,0,,A warship is arriving at the harbor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:19.17,Flashback inception,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:26.11,Flashback inception,,0,0,0,,I've seen that logo before!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:29.35,Flashback inception,,0,0,0,,Cipher Pol Aegis Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:36.10,Flashback inception,,0,0,0,,They're the Government officials who work directly under the World Nobles!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:37.32,Flashback inception,,0,0,0,,Why are they here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:42.36,Flashback inception,,0,0,0,,Remain calm, citizens of Dressrosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:49.44,Flashback inception,,0,0,0,,Regarding the report on Doflamingo's abdication from the throne and the Seven Warlords of the Sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:51.65,Flashback inception,,0,0,0,,that spread all over the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:56.31,Flashback inception,,0,0,0,,It was a mistake. Just a false report.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:10:06.35,Flashback inception,,0,0,0,,And, the news of this will spread around the world in the extra edition, today at 3 in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:09.46,Flashback inception,,0,0,0,,It's going to be a secret until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:12.06,Flashback inception,,0,0,0,,You mustn't tell anybody about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:18.32,Flashback inception,,0,0,0,,All citizens should keep living peacefully as if nothing has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:28.06,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,What's with this cunning deceit that seems plotted by a fox?! {This one CR has totally ignored and put stupid "What's with this? I'm so confused!". The line i wrote seems better and the most thing, it's far more accurate. The Black Adder line: Is It A Cunning Plan?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:29.88,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,The World Government?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:33.21,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,It's beyond a Warlord's control, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:37.51,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:43.12,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,scared of Doflamingo so I can't run away, but maybe you people can get away in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:49.03,Captions,,0,0,220,,{\fad(400,0)}Present time\NGreen Bit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:50.83,Main,,0,0,0,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:56.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow! What's this? Nico Robin's upper half popped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:57.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Nico-{\i0}ya{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:11:00.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I was listening to the conversation. It was Sanji, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.71,0:11:04.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are your real body and Nose-{\i0}ya{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:08.90,Main,,0,0,0,,If what Black Foot-{\i0}ya{\i0} was talking about is true, the deal with Doflamingo is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:10.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh, off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:13.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, what's gonna happen to my hand-over?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:15.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Nico-{\i0}ya{\i0}! Summon Nose-{\i0}ya{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:17.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's get off of the island now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:21.73,Main,,0,0,0,,The thing is, we're under Green Bit right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:22.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Under?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:26.07,Main,,0,0,0,,We had some trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.07,0:11:28.90,Main,,0,0,0,,But both Usopp and I are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:32.96,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't help you, but if you're gonna escape, go without us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:36.37,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll go to the harbor where we agreed to meet up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:38.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, understo{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.18,Main,,0,0,0,,T-The Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:51.79,Main,,0,0,0,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:52.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.56,Main,,0,0,0,,You guys, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:06.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Joker!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:13.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:17.13,Main,,0,0,0,,You've done well, all things considered!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:21.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect to see a Navy Admiral here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.56,0:12:26.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Since I'm no longer a Warlord, I'm scared as hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:29.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:37.10,Captions,,0,0,220,,{\fad(100,0)}At the same time in Dressrosa\N"Corrida Colosseum"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:46.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, all the competitors of\NBlock C are finally in the arena!¬Å
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.14,Captions,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1004,332)}Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:46.51,Captions,,0,0,0,,{\pos(212,460)}Gladiator
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:49.25,Main,,0,0,0,,139 warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:47.85,Captions,,0,0,0,,{\pos(258,298)}Assassin
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.25,Captions,,0,0,0,,{\pos(966,470)}Bounty Hunter
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:50.62,Captions,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1032,490)}Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:51.72,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a battle royale!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:51.98,Captions,,0,0,0,,{\pos(376,402)}Boxer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:56.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Who's gonna win this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.35,Captions,,0,0,0,,{\pos(538,468)}Bullfighting
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:54.72,Captions,,0,0,0,,{\pos(162,240)}Former Pirate
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:56.09,Captions,,0,0,0,,{\pos(374,452)}Giant Warrior
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:57.92,Captions,,0,0,0,,{\pos(970,470)}Assassin
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:05.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, the battle is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:11.69,Main,,0,0,0,,You're already in the ring? Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:14.97,Main,,0,0,0,,You're in Block D, aren't you, Cavendish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.97,0:13:16.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to break in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:18.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:20.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Cut it out! Or you'll be eliminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:30.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:37.86,Captions,,0,0,220,,{\fad(500,0)}Simultaneously\NAll around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:41.48,Main,,0,0,0,,An extra edition?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:43.57,Main,,0,0,0,,It seems like a correction about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:45.48,Main,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:49.59,Main,,0,0,0,,The big news about Doflamingo was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:51.24,Sash,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1082,574)}I'm a Candidate for\NWarlord of the Sea
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:53.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Incorrect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:55.85,Main,,0,0,0,,That's insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.37,0:14:06.39,Captions,,0,0,220,,{\fad(250,0)}Green Bit
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.39,0:14:09.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You used the authority of the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:15.70,Main,,0,0,0,,You fooled the whole world... only to deceive ten of us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:25.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Usually, the more spectacular the magic show, the simpler the trick behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:25.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:29.68,Main,,0,0,0,,"There is no way he would do such a ridiculous thing."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:36.44,Main,,0,0,0,,People usually have a preconceived idea\Nor an assumption, which leaves a blind spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.49,0:14:39.83,Main,,0,0,0,,You're a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:43.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if you're a Warlord of the Sea and a king,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:49.43,Main,,0,0,0,,you don't have the power to spread a lie all over the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:57.70,Main,,0,0,0,,The only people in this world who have the power to do such a ridiculous thing are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:15:00.03,Main,,0,0,0,,the Celestial Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:05.20,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,You don't know about Joker's past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:08.49,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,And that will cost you your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:14.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me... you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:22.45,Main,,0,0,0,,It's bit more complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:23.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:29.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:32.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been wanting to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:40.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Joker! Kick this guy's ass alrea{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:44.39,Main,,0,0,0,,There is no way I'm gonna hand him over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:47.79,Main,,0,0,0,,You didn't follow any of my terms!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:51.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Doflamingo! This deal is off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:55.30,Main,,0,0,0,,No! W-What're you talking about, you fool?! We got this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:16:02.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that how you talk to your boss after 10 years of silence?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.28,0:16:04.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Leave him, Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:07.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Caesar is one of my precious subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:08.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Jo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:13.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Issho-{\i0}san{\i0}, it's Caesar Clown who is with Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:17.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. He is the scientist from the poison gas incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:17.96,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Joker!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.96,0:16:24.01,Main,,0,0,0,,But if he is that Warlord's subordinate, he won't be charged.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:24.93,Main,,0,0,0,,They'll grant him amnesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:27.73,Main,,0,0,0,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:33.07,Main,,0,0,0,,You are Fujitora, appointed as a Navy admiral by the World Military Draft.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:35.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I've heard about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:40.46,Main,,0,0,0,,They say you and Ryokugyu are insanely powerful monsters, with unquestionable power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:40.46,Note,,0,0,0,,Ryokugyu: Green Bull
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:42.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, why thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:46.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:53.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm still new to the Navy so it's hard for me to understand what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:17:03.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't have enough evidence yet, but I have received information about you breaking the rules as a Warlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:09.27,Main,,0,0,0,,The man right there was calling you "Joker"; is that your nickname?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:18.58,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want to investigate me, you have to be really determined and collect enough evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:23.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, what's the Navy's decision about Law's punishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.46,0:17:34.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Regarding the news about you and the wanted pirates, the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:37.59,Main,,0,0,0,,if you have formed an alliance as reported in the news, you're guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.59,0:17:41.94,Main,,0,0,0,,If they have become your subordinates, Law-{\i0}san{\i0}, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:43.94,Main,,0,0,0,,not guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:48.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Our mission depends on your response.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:53.88,Main,,0,0,0,,We may have to arrest you and the Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:59.19,Main,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what kind of decision is that?! He can just get away by lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:06.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Our original plan is ruined.\NNow {\i1}we're{\i0} being targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:10.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Even if I take this matter to Dressrosa,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:12.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,the situation will only worsen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.47,0:18:14.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,I need to buy some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:19.59,Main,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats are not working under me! It's an alliance as the article states!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.86,0:18:24.38,Main,,0,0,0,,You're such a clumsy man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:28.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, we have to strip you of your title.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:32.61,Main,,0,0,0,,It'd be if the news ended here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:48.76,Main,,0,0,0,,You're kidding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:53.56,Main,,0,0,0,,A meteorite!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:55.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I-It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:01.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop joking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:02.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:03.81,Main,,0,0,0,,A meteorite is falling on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:49.91,Main,,0,0,0,,A-Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:51.73,Main,,0,0,0,,W-Where's Issho-{\i0}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:55.00,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! What just happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:03.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Only the three spots that they're standing on are untouched!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:09.59,Main,,0,0,0,,How did the Fleet Admiral train you?! You damn stray dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:13.06,Main,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if he can see or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:17.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you. I simply wanted to test your skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:22.10,Captions,,0,0,240,,{\fad(500,0)}"Dressrosa"\NTeam Franky
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:24.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Flower Field?! Are you gonna go on a picnic?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:28.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Speaking of picnics, where did you wonder off to, Sanji?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:30.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.53,0:20:32.24,Main,,0,0,0,,in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:37.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's nice to hear. By the way, I think I can find the factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:38.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Really?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:43.12,Main,,0,0,0,,But unfortunately, we can't just destroy it and get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:47.09,Main,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be a much bigger task than we expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:50.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! We don't allow credit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.79,0:20:53.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Somebody, catch that toy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:55.61,Main,,0,0,0,,He ran away without paying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:01.41,Main,,0,0,0,,We don't have time! Doflamingo was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:06.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I just read the extra edition. He sure fooled us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:11.01,Main,,0,0,0,,If he gets Caesar back, our entire plan ends in failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.01,0:21:14.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's destroy the factory and put his nose out of joint!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:18.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyway, come meet us at the Flower Field!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.41,0:21:21.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you what's with that fairytale-ish place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:24.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By the way, I can't reach Nami-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.96,0:21:30.04,Main,,0,0,0,,You still think she's a weakling? She's gonna be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:33.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Brook and Monster Chopper are with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.65,0:21:35.53,Main,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.53,0:21:37.01,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? What's wrong?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:41.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Violet-{\i0}chan{\i0}, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:43.98,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a broadcast from the Colosseum.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.98,0:21:47.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The unknown gladiator, Lucy, is pretty strong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.15,0:21:48.55,Main,,0,0,0,,He's small but tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:55.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Franky, you won't believe this but, Luffy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.85,0:21:59.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's fighting in a competition now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:03.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Why did you let him?!\NYou should've kept an eye on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:05.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're in no place to judge me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:09.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Black Foot, I have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.21,0:22:11.18,Main,,0,0,0,,My men are coming after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:14.59,Main,,0,0,0,,You want to go to the secret factory, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.59,0:22:16.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Here is a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:19.12,Main,,0,0,0,,It's disguised as "Toy House."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.12,0:22:21.62,Main,,0,0,0,,But that's the factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.62,0:22:25.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, I can't take this!\NIf you help me more, you're gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.38,0:22:29.87,Main,,0,0,0,,You're a funny man. It doesn't make any difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.87,0:22:34.47,Main,,0,0,0,,It seems like the executives already know that I betrayed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.76,0:22:39.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Violet-{\i0}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.02,0:22:42.86,Main,,0,0,0,,The western harbor! Meet me there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.86,0:22:45.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Hide yourself there and wait until I get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.19,0:22:47.18,Main,,0,0,0,,That's our rendezvous point!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.65,0:22:54.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I will help you get away from here at any price!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:23:00.36,Main,,0,0,0,,You really are a good-for-nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.50,0:23:09.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry to interrupt, you good-for-nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.47,0:23:12.80,Main,,0,0,0,,You fool! Where did you come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.80,0:23:14.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Violet-{\i0}chan{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.02,0:23:16.93,Main,,0,0,0,,You have to beat them all up first.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:18.71,Main,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.77,0:23:27.89,Main,,0,0,0,,A-Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.89,0:23:30.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you do it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.13,0:23:35.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do anything because they're holding Kanjuro as a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.23,0:23:40.35,Main,,0,0,0,,You have to come with me, Sanji-{\i0}dono{\i0}! To the place called Toy House!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:43.85,Main,,0,0,0,,That's where they are keeping my fellow samurai, Kanjuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.85,0:23:45.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know where it is, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.97,0:23:50.51,Captions,,0,0,190,,{\fad(500,0)}Back on "Green Bit"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.61,0:23:53.38,Captions,,0,0,190,,{\fad(500,0)}Beneath the forest
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.48,0:23:56.28,Captions,,0,0,190,,{\fad(500,0)}Tontatta Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.28,0:23:59.18,Main,,0,0,0,,What's causing the ground to shake?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.70,0:24:01.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,It must be Law and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.20,0:24:06.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn! I don't wanna die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.16,0:24:07.16,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.16,0:24:08.99,Main,,0,0,0,,The hero is getting upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.38,0:24:16.44,Main,,0,0,0,,J-Just kidding. The truth is the shake was...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.44,0:24:18.14,Main,,0,0,0,,caused by my Haki.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.14,0:24:24.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Haki?! Isn't that the technique that you used to beat 50,000 villains on Fishman Island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.51,0:24:26.08,Main,,0,0,0,,As expected from our hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.24,0:24:29.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Your energy can shake up this kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.98,0:24:32.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, please eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.77,0:24:36.85,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a Fighting Fish. It's big and a close relative of the goldfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.85,0:24:38.13,Main,,0,0,0,,A Fighting Fish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.13,0:24:38.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.61,0:24:45.12,Main,,0,0,0,,It's good! I didn't expect it to taste this good!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.12,0:24:48.88,Main,,0,0,0,,It tastes like the sea monster that I killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.12,0:24:51.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,As I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.03,0:24:55.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,they're the ones who caught the Fighting Fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.41,0:24:59.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,What kind of strength is that?\NThe Dwarf tribe is super strong, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.18,0:25:04.08,Main,,0,0,0,,They're pretty big so they can provide food for the kingdom for months.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.08,0:25:08.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Usoland, you're a Big Human so I guess you can eat a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.79,0:25:14.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffyland who belongs to my fighting force, the Usolanders,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.03,0:25:16.18,Main,,0,0,0,,can eat the whole fish with one bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.83,0:25:19.38,Main,,0,0,0,,What's an Usoland?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.38,0:25:22.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Look. Doesn't that look familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.80,0:25:28.29,Main,,0,0,0,,He's from the picture book that we read in Jaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.78,0:25:37.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that a statue of Montblanc Noland?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.05,0:25:37.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.13,0:25:42.99,Main,,0,0,0,,You know him too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.99,0:25:49.66,Main,,0,0,0,,He was a Big Human botanist who came to visit this kingdom 400 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.66,0:25:53.46,Main,,0,0,0,,At that time, villainous Big Humans were devastating the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.46,0:25:56.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Seeing that our ancestors were troubled,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.70,0:26:00.58,Main,,0,0,0,,he fought alongside us and led them to victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.58,0:26:03.48,Main,,0,0,0,,He became the legendary hero of the Tontatta Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.48,0:26:09.25,Main,,0,0,0,,When Usoland said his name and told us that he's one of his descendants,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.25,0:26:10.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I was speechless!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.33,0:26:13.45,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,L-Look at my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.45,0:26:16.60,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,This chestnut-shaped head is the proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.60,0:26:17.57,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.57,0:26:18.86,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,The chestnut-shaped head!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.16,0:26:22.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't have any idea! I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.76,0:26:24.30,Main,,0,0,0,,You're a horrible person.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.30,0:26:27.23,Main,,0,0,0,,You were saved by it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.01,0:26:31.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's eat, get some gifts and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.07,0:26:34.20,Main,,0,0,0,,This must be destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.20,0:26:36.44,Main,,0,0,0,,To see them today.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.73,0:26:39.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.13,0:26:43.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Today is the day we vowed to fight Doflamingo...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.98,0:26:48.85,Main,,0,0,0,,and after 400 years, a legendary hero has came along again!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.54,0:26:55.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Usoland! After you finish eating, let's go to the Flower Field via the underground passage!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.16,0:26:56.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.98,0:26:59.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.68,0:27:02.30,Main,,0,0,0,,In Dressrosa, where we're gonna fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.30,0:27:06.05,Main,,0,0,0,,the commander and our fellow soldiers of King Riku's Army are expecting us!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.05,0:27:08.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.27,0:27:12.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Please stand at the forefront and lead us!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.45,0:27:15.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's destroy the Donquixote Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.69,0:27:17.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.02,0:27:20.27,Main,,0,0,0,,With Usoland, we're unbeatable!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.27,0:27:21.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.55,0:27:23.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Our hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.70,0:27:27.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Usoland!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.46,0:27:37.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Usoland!{\i0}
